erickcoffeehouse.pantheonsite.io/2016/12/01/1-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(20,5,'2016-12-02 01:25:14','2016-12-02 01:25:14','<b><span style=\"margin: 0px; color: #c0a419; font-family: \'Bookman Old Style\',serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Ginkgo Coffeehouse on Snelling</span></b>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"margin: 0px; color: #6a6c6e; font-family: \'Bookman Old Style\',serif; font-size: 12pt;\">The original GINKGO location has been open for over 20 years! It is characterized by the large, comfortable seating area. It also offers a children’s play area and two patios.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"margin: 0px; color: #6a6c6e; font-family: \'Bookman Old Style\',serif; font-size: 12pt;\">This location is home to the music and special events that have made GINKGO a St. Paul destination. GINKGO Coffeehouse on Snelling sells numerous retail items, including exceptional greeting cards and toys for kids of all ages. Soups, sandwiches, lasagna, burritos, and some baked goods are made and sold on the premises. Other goodies are brought in from local bakeries.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"margin: 0px; color: #6a6c6e; font-family: \'Bookman Old Style\',serif; font-size: 12pt;\"> </span>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; color: #6f4e37; font-family: \'Bookman Old Style\',serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Hours of operation:</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; color: #6f4e37; font-family: \'Bookman Old Style\',serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Monday through Thursday, 6:15 am – 10 pm</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; color: #6f4e37; font-family: \'Bookman Old Style\',serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Friday, 6:15 am – 11 pm</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; color: #6f4e37; font-family: \'Bookman Old Style\',serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Saturday, 6:30 am – 11pm</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; color: #6f4e37; font-family: \'Bookman Old Style\',serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Sunday, 7:00 am – 10 pm</span></p>\r\n<span style=\"margin: 0px; color: #6a6c6e; font-family: \'Bookman Old Style\',serif; font-size: 12pt;\"> </span>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; color: #6f4e37; font-family: \'Bookman Old Style\',serif; font-size: 12pt;\">721 N. Snelling Ave.</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; color: #6f4e37; font-family: \'Bookman Old Style\',serif; font-size: 12pt;\">St. Paul MN 55104</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; color: #6f4e37; font-family: \'Bookman Old Style\',serif; font-size: 12pt;\">651-645-2647</span></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[huge_it_maps id=\"1\"]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b><span style=\"margin: 0px; color: #c0a419; font-family: \'Bookman Old Style\',serif; font-size: 12pt;\">GINKGO Coffee Bar &amp; Deli, GardenView Medical Building</span></b>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"margin: 0px; color: #6a6c6e; font-family: \'Bookman Old Style\',serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Located in the Gardenview Medial Building, this location is on your way to Children\'s Hospital, when you park in the Red Ramp. Located on the 1st floor, we offer a wide range of sandwiches, homemade soups, espresso drinks, whole fruit smoothies, and other beverages. Friendly staff and great food!</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"margin: 0px; color: #6a6c6e; font-family: \'Bookman Old Style\',serif; font-size: 12pt;\"> </span>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; color: #6f4e37; font-family: \'Bookman Old Style\',serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Hours of operation:</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; color: #6f4e37; font-family: \'Bookman Old Style\',serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Monday through Friday, 6:30 am - 4:30 pm</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; color: #6f4e37; font-family: \'Bookman Old Style\',serif; font-size: 12pt;\">347 N. Smith Ave.</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; color: #6f4e37; font-family: \'Bookman Old Style\',serif; font-size: 12pt;\">St. Paul, MN 55102</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; color: #6f4e37; font-family: \'Bookman Old Style\',serif; font-size: 12pt;\">651-220-6200</span></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[huge_it_maps id=\"2\"]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b><span style=\"margin: 0px; color: #c0a419; font-family: \'Bookman Old Style\',serif; font-size: 12pt;\">GINKGO Coffee &amp; Smoothie Bar, St. Joseph\'s Hospital</span></b>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"margin: 0px; color: #6a6c6e; font-family: \'Bookman Old Style\',serif; font-size: 12pt;\">GINKGO Coffee and Smoothie Bar is located in the beautiful new DePaul Tower, at St. Joseph\'s Hospital. With a lovely garden and patio, and a comfortable seating area and fireplace inside, this is a great location for lunch, even if you\'re not visiting the hospital. It is located just inside the patient drop-off/pick-up loop on 10th Stree, at the corner of St. Peter and 10th. It\'s a fast, friendly, and convenient stop for those already in the hospital building as well as those passing by.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"margin: 0px; color: #6a6c6e; font-family: \'Bookman Old Style\',serif; font-size: 12pt;\"> </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"margin: 0px; color: #6a6c6e; font-family: \'Bookman Old Style\',serif; font-size: 12pt;\">GINKGO Coffee and Smoothie Bar serves fresh-baked pastries, fresh sandwiches and soup, salads, and a wide range of beverages including fruit smoothies and espresso drinks.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"margin: 0px; color: #6a6c6e; font-family: \'Bookman Old Style\',serif; font-size: 12pt;\"> </span>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; color: #6f4e37; font-family: \'Bookman Old Style\',serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Hours of operation:</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; color: #6f4e37; font-family: \'Bookman Old Style\',serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Monday through Friday, 6:30 am - 8:00 pm</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; color: #6f4e37; font-family: \'Bookman Old Style\',serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Saturday, 7:30 am - 2:30 pm</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; color: #6f4e37; font-family: \'Bookman Old Style\',serif; font-size: 12pt;\">(may be able to serve coffee as early as 6:30am)</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; color: #6f4e37; font-family: \'Bookman Old Style\',serif; font-size: 12pt;\">45 10th St. West</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; color: #6f4e37; font-family: \'Bookman Old Style\',serif; font-size: 12pt;\">St. Paul, MN 55102</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; color: #6f4e37; font-family: \'Bookman Old Style\',serif; font-size: 12pt;\">651-326-3766</span></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[huge_it_maps id=\"3\"]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b><span style=\"margin: 0px; color: #c0a419; font-family: \'Bookman Old Style\',serif; font-size: 12pt;\">GINKGO Coffee &amp; Deli Bar, Gillette Children\'s Hospital</span></b>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"margin: 0px; color: #6a6c6e; font-family: \'Bookman Old Style\',serif; font-size: 12pt;\">GINKGO Coffee Bar &amp; Deli is located on the 4th floor of Gillette Children\'s Hospital (this is the main entrance, level D from the parking ramp). Seating is available at the coffee bar. Easily accessible, this location offers the same homemade sandwiches and soups, and beverages. It also offers a children\'s menu and soft serve ice cream!</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"margin: 0px; color: #6a6c6e; font-family: \'Bookman Old Style\',serif; font-size: 12pt;\"> </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"margin: 0px; color: #6a6c6e; font-family: \'Bookman Old Style\',serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Only a short walk when coming from Region\'s Hospital (all indoors), our food is made with fresh ingredients, and there is something for everyone. Hours of Operation: Monday through Friday, 6:30 am - 4:30 pm.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"margin: 0px; color: #6a6c6e; font-family: \'Bookman Old Style\',serif; font-size: 12pt;\"> </span>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><span st