hes sport a wide variety of locally grown produce such as tomatoes, lettuce, cucumbers, and onions. Our soups are often made with locally grown squash, zucchini, onions, and cauliflower, to name a few.','Fair Trade and Organic Products','','inherit','closed','closed','','39-revision-v1','','','2016-12-02 02:37:34','2016-12-02 02:37:34','',39,'http://dev-teamerickcoffeehouse.pantheonsite.io/2016/12/02/39-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(46,5,'2016-12-02 02:39:16','2016-12-02 02:39:16','','About Us','','publish','closed','closed','','about-us','','','2016-12-02 02:39:16','2016-12-02 02:39:16','',0,'http://dev-teamerickcoffeehouse.pantheonsite.io/?page_id=46',0,'page','',0),(47,5,'2016-12-02 02:39:16','2016-12-02 02:39:16','','About Us','','inherit','closed','closed','','46-revision-v1','','','2016-12-02 02:39:16','2016-12-02 02:39:16','',46,'http://dev-teamerickcoffeehouse.pantheonsite.io/2016/12/02/46-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(48,5,'2016-12-02 02:40:08','2016-12-02 02:40:08','','Music and Upcoming Events','','publish','closed','closed','','music-and-events','','','2016-12-10 08:06:09','2016-12-10 08:06:09','',0,'http://dev-teamerickcoffeehouse.pantheonsite.io/?page_id=48',0,'page','',0),(49,5,'2016-12-02 02:40:08','2016-12-02 02:40:08','','Music and Upcoming Events','','inherit','closed','closed','','48-revision-v1','','','2016-12-02 02:40:08','2016-12-02 02:40:08','',48,'http://dev-teamerickcoffeehouse.pantheonsite.io/2016/12/02/48-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(50,5,'2016-12-02 02:40:24','2016-12-02 02:40:24','<b><span style=\"margin: 0px; color: #5a352d; font-family: \'Bookman Old Style\',serif; font-size: 20pt;\">Beverages</span></b>\r\n\r\n<b><span style=\"margin: 0px; color: #c0a419; font-family: \'Bookman Old Style\',serif; font-size: 16pt;\">Brewed Coffee</span></b>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"margin: 0px; color: #6a6c6e; font-family: \'Bookman Old Style\',serif; font-size: 12pt;\">(includes flavored coffee; all are roasted daily by Alakef Coffee Roaster